Subject: [PATCH v9 04/19] spi: spi-mtk-nor: reject DTR ops
Date:   Mon, 25 May 2020 14:45:29 +0530
Message-ID: <20200525091544.17270-5-p.yadav@ti.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.25.0
